<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fa;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #ef4444; /* red-500 */
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 40px 30px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .content h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
      color: #1f2937;
    }
    .content p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #4b5563;
    }
    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 35px 0;
    }
    .reset-button {
      background-color: #ef4444;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .reset-button:hover {
      background-color: #dc2626;
    }
    .fallback-link {
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      word-break: break-all;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #6b7280;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
    }
    .token-box {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #f3f4f6;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #111827;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    .warning {
      color: #ef4444;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account. If you made this request, please click the button below to set a new password.</p>

      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="<%= resetLink %>" class="reset-button">Reset Password</a>
      </div>

      <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following link into your browser:</p>
      <div class="fallback-link">
        <a href="<%= resetLink %>" style="color: #ef4444;"><%= resetLink %></a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px;" class="warning">If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have concerns.</p>
      <p>Thanks,<br>The Application Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Our Application. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>This email was sent to <%= email || 'your email' %>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
